name: Vs Piglin (Full Week)
description:
Boyfriend travels to the nether!

Note: I didn't make the week, I just ported it! This was originally made for the FNF in MC engine, please support the original developers! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5UIrgtntfnw

Proof I have permission to post this

Boyfriend travels to the nether, but he isn't wearing any gold... To get back to the overworld in one piece, he'll have to rap battle a Piglin! 

This custom week features 3 new songs, based off of music discs from Minecraft.
